{{#> layout}}
  <div class="hero animate-fade-in">
    <img src="{{siteUrl}}/images/abandoned-cart-banner.jpg" alt="Your Cart is Waiting" class="hero-image">
    <div class="hero-overlay">
      <h1 class="hero-title">Your Art Selections Are Waiting</h1>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="animate-slide-in" style="animation-delay: 0.1s;">
    <p>Dear {{user.firstName}},</p>
    
    <p>We noticed you left some beautiful art pieces in your shopping cart. Your selections are still saved and waiting for you to complete your purchase.</p>
    
    <div class="button-container">
      <a href="{{cartUrl}}" class="button">Return to Your Cart</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="animate-slide-in" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
    <h2>Your Saved Items</h2>
    
    {{#each cart.items}}
      <div class="product-card">
        <img src="{{product.images.[0]}}" alt="{{product.name}}" class="product-image">
        <div class="product-details">
          <h3 class="product-name">{{product.name}}</h3>
          <p class="product-price">{{formatCurrency product.price}} Ã— {{quantity}}</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    {{/each}}
    
    <div class="summary-box">
      <div class="summary-row">
        <span>Subtotal:</span>
        <span>{{formatCurrency cart.subtotal}}</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <p>These items are popular and may sell out soon. Complete your purchase now to ensure you don't miss out on these unique artistic creations.</p>
    
    <div class="button-container">
      <a href="{{cartUrl}}" class="button">Complete Your Purchase</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="animate-slide-in" style="animation-delay: 0.3s;">
    <h2>Need Help?</h2>
    
    <p>If you have any questions about the items in your cart or need assistance with your purchase, our team is here to help. Contact us at {{shopEmail}} or call us at {{shopPhone}}.</p>
    
    <p>Thank you for considering Raymond Arts for your artistic needs. We hope to see you back soon!</p>
    
    <p>
      Warm regards,<br>
      The Raymond Arts Team
    </p>
  </div>
{{/layout}}